{"id": 2553, "genre": 1001, "title": "在你心中，哪些元素才能让城市更有特色？", "description": "是什么让一座城市在你眼中显得“不一样”？（题图来自：iStock ©️ Antikwar）", "record_count": 4130, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181008163941T04MmyIqti1fxNhJ.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-10T03:16:43Z", "options": [{"id": 303104, "content": "书店文化   城市的文明建设", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460077}, {"id": 303872, "content": "城市园林绿地，文明的人文景观", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469707}, {"id": 303105, "content": "书店文化   城市的文明建设", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460077}, {"id": 303106, "content": "早点铺子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466963}, {"id": 303362, "content": "古味的建筑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1447913}, {"id": 304130, "content": "城市肌理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313812}, {"id": 303107, "content": "不可思议的美食", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466971}, {"id": 303875, "content": "没有人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299461}, {"id": 303108, "content": "科学的规划，但不失人情味", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408948}, {"id": 303364, "content": "保留旧事物，设计新事物来诠释发展旧事物", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467867}, {"id": 303109, "content": "生活方式。比如我们兰州人就爱挖烂酒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056087}, {"id": 303621, "content": "绝对是方言", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1468398}, {"id": 303110, "content": "城市小吃的特色，老味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466984}, {"id": 303111, "content": "不一样的民族风情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466985}, {"id": 303112, "content": "公共设施对应地段应用形式美学的设计，干净的蔬菜市场，以及没有机械的人工服务商场。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1305745}, {"id": 303113, "content": "实际上每个城市都有特色，不过一二级商圈确实哪里都一样，所以，要是有哪个城市商圈和别人不一样的话，算是特色吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450211}, {"id": 303114, "content": "有趣的灵魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466991}, {"id": 304650, "content": "嗯，有一些长期性的文化活动，比如电影节，戏剧节等", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469280}, {"id": 303115, "content": "有趣的灵魂", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466991}, {"id": 303116, "content": "不用排队2小时能吃到的百年老字号", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467001}, {"id": 305932, "content": "独特的市井文化  特有的地方味道  生活在这个城市里人与人间的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479134}, {"id": 303118, "content": "青岛与啤酒，火锅与重庆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467004}, {"id": 303119, "content": "建筑与人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254970}, {"id": 303120, "content": "老人的生活方式\n早点铺子\n方言", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154351}, {"id": 303121, "content": "城市在民生方面明显的强项", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1440360}, {"id": 303122, "content": "每天的一日三餐\n普通人的生活方式\n我在那里的生活方式", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1442451}, {"id": 303123, "content": "属于这座城市独有的东西。文化或者建筑等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374091}, {"id": 303124, "content": "满街道充满的火锅味", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458770}, {"id": 303125, "content": "小城市的小道道\n和山里面", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467040}, {"id": 303126, "content": "建筑物", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1452949}, {"id": 303127, "content": "我是扬州人，我们的市中心是一个类似天坛的阁楼，叫文昌阁，于是没有十字路口，只有环形路口，与世界上所有城市都不一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404922}, {"id": 303129, "content": "真正的科技集合之地，能够轻易切换城市主题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467048}, {"id": 303898, "content": "我来看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470070}, {"id": 304666, "content": "老的不方便通车的建筑群", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240486}, {"id": 303131, "content": "干净和秩序\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597684}, {"id": 303132, "content": "一个城市老城区的道路间距和居民楼间距", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262509}, {"id": 303133, "content": "风土人情，古建筑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467085}, {"id": 303389, "content": "能够让人静心阅读的书店", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437040}, {"id": 303134, "content": "公共厕所 如果一个城市的公共厕所很干净，那那个城市得居民也是爱干净的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466041}, {"id": 304158, "content": "小吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1471969}, {"id": 303903, "content": "悠久的历史", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911164}, {"id": 308256, "content": "每个城市人们之间的沟通方式，以及待人接物的礼貌程度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490109}, {"id": 303137, "content": "文化底蕴吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441975}, {"id": 303905, "content": "标志性的建筑 当地文化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470144}, {"id": 303138, "content": "人情.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434374}, {"id": 304674, "content": "有地方特色的美食小吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473677}, {"id": 303139, "content": "有当地居民的古民居 古村落，里面有热气腾腾的早点铺子，理发店，杂货店这些生活化的事物，而不是商业改建过的~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284195}, {"id": 303141, "content": "老城区 旧建筑\n而不是翻新后的复古", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397304}, {"id": 303397, "content": "风土人情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467868}, {"id": 303909, "content": "食物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469533}]}